server - string
ncores - int
program - string

list(list(server1, ncores1, program1),
     list(server2, ncores2, program2),
     ...,
     list(servern, ncoresn, programn))

default:
list(list("localhost", system("cpu"), ""))

Any values left out are replaced by
"localhost", [all cpus on this server] and "" respectively,
except for ssi:tcp links, where the default program is
the return value of system("Singular").

Note that the shortcut list("any string") defines the server
rather than the program to be used.
